ZH: 我的班级里有三十五个学生。
EN: There are thirty-five students in my class.

ZH: 班级里的学生们都非常友好。
EN: The students in the class are very friendly.

ZH: 我们的班级老师是一位年轻的女士。
EN: Our class teacher is a young lady.

ZH: 班级里有各种不同的人才。
EN: There are various talents in the class.

ZH: 这个班级的成绩一直很出色。
EN: This class has always had excellent results.

ZH: 我们班级的氛围非常轻松愉快。
EN: The atmosphere in our class is very relaxed and pleasant.

ZH: 请不要在班级里说脏话。
EN: Please do not use foul language in the class.

ZH: 我们班级要进行一次团队建设活动。
EN: Our class is going to have a team-building activity.

ZH: 班级里的学生们都互相帮助。
EN: The students in the class help each other.

ZH: 我们班级有一个很好的学习氛围。
EN: Our class has a great learning atmosphere.

ZH: 班级里有一位特别优秀的学生。
EN: There is a particularly outstanding student in the class.

ZH: 班级里有很多不同的人格特征。
EN: There are many different personality traits in the class.

ZH: 我们的班级每年都有一次班会。
EN: Our class has a class meeting every year.

ZH: 班级里有很多有趣的人。
EN: There are many interesting individuals in the class.

ZH: 班级里有一个很受欢迎的人。
EN: There is a very popular person in the class.

ZH: 我们的班级每年会举办一次运动会。
EN: Our class holds a sports day every year.

ZH: 班级里的学生们都非常努力。
EN: The students in the class are very hardworking.

ZH: 我们班级的同学们都很认真对待学习。
EN: The classmates in our class take their studies very seriously.

ZH: 班级里的同学们都很团结。
EN: The classmates in the class are very united.

ZH: 我们班级的学风非常好。
EN: The academic atmosphere in our class is very good.
